      <li><strong>Small Indian-made (60cm cooking floor, 2–3 pizzas):</strong> ₹80,000 – ₹1,20,000</li>
      <li><strong>Medium Indian-made (80–90cm floor, 3–5 pizzas):</strong> ₹1,20,000 – ₹2,00,000</li>
      <li><strong>Large Indian-made (120cm floor, 5–7 pizzas):</strong> ₹1,80,000 – ₹2,80,000</li>
