      <li><strong>Single-deck, 2-pizza, Indian brand (LPG/PNG):</strong> ₹60,000 – ₹95,000</li>
      <li><strong>Single-deck, 4-pizza, Indian brand:</strong> ₹85,000 – ₹1,40,000</li>
      <li><strong>Double-deck, 4+4 pizza, Indian brand:</strong> ₹1,40,000 – ₹2,00,000</li>
      <li><strong>Single-deck, imported (Moretti Forni, Italforni), 4-pizza:</strong> ₹1,50,000 – ₹2,20,000</li>
