    <h2>3. Electric Pizza Ovens: Best for Cloud Kitchens and Urban Restaurants</h2>

    <p>Electric pizza deck ovens offer the most precise temperature control of any pizza oven type. You set 380°C and you get 380°C, maintained consistently across the deck. There's no gas supply to manage, no smoke, and installation is as simple as a 3-phase electrical connection. For cloud kitchens, delivery-focused operations, and urban restaurants where a gas connection or wood-fire ventilation is impractical, electric ovens are the default choice.</p>

