    <h2>8. Full Cost Comparison: 5-Year Total Cost of Ownership</h2>

    <p>Purchase price is only part of the story. Here's a 5-year total cost of ownership comparison for a medium-volume pizzeria doing 50 pizzas per service, 6 services per week:</p>

